OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Major Labour
OL,4,Closses across North West
OL,6,FThe Labour Party has suffered major
OL,7,Flosses across the North West following
OL,8,FThursday's local elections.
OL,10,FThe results have been worse than
OL,11,Fexpected for Labour, with losses in
OL,12,Fsome of the party's key strongholds.
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer's party went into the
OL,15,Flocal elections expected to lose up to
OL,16,F1,850 councillors, with senior figures
OL,17,Fdescribing the contest as "tough".
OL,19,FThe polls closed at 10pm on Thursday 7
OL,20,FMay, with results expected to be
OL,21,Fdeclared throughout today.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
