OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Major Labour
OL,4,Closses across North West
OL,6,FSpeaking about Reform's success across
OL,7,Fthe country, party leader Nigel Farage
OL,8,Fsaid he is "thrilled and delighted" at
OL,9,Fthe results so far, describing it as
OL,10,F"a historic shift".
OL,12,FHe said: "If you go to Merseyside and
OL,13,FGreater Manchester, have a look at
OL,14,Fwhat we have achieved overnight
OL,15,Falready in results. Tameside being an
OL,16,Fexample, we won all the seats that
OL,17,Fwere up overnight.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
