PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778259959
OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Major Labour
OL,4,Closses across North West
OL,6,FTameside Council - which has been a
OL,7,Fsolid Labour area since 1979 - has
OL,8,Fbeen left with no group large enough
OL,9,Fto have overall control, as Reform UK
OL,10,Fwon 18 of the 19 seats up for election.
OL,12,FIt was in this area that the
OL,13,Fresignation of MP Andrew Gwynne led to
OL,14,Fthe Gorton and Denton by-election-
OL,15,F which saw the Green Party win their
OL,16,Ffifth seat, while Labour fell to third
OL,17,Fbehind Reform.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778259959
OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Major Labour
OL,4,Closses across North West
OL,6,FHalton - which is home to the Runcorn
OL,7,Fand Helsby parliamentary seat, won by
OL,8,FReform from Labour in a by-election
OL,9,Flast year - has remained a Labour
OL,10,Fmajority, despite Reform gaining 16
OL,11,Fseats.
OL,13,FReform also won all but one of the
OL,14,Fseats available in Wigan, where Labour
OL,15,Flost 22 councillors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778259959
OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Major Labour
OL,4,Closses across North West
OL,6,FThe Conservatives also lost their one
OL,7,Fremaining seat in Wigan, as Reform won
OL,8,F24 seats on the authority, bringing
OL,9,Fits total to 25, with an Independent
OL,10,Fcandidate picking up the remaining
OL,11,Fseat on offer.
OL,13,FLabour managed to keep control in
OL,14,FSalford - a majority the party has had
OL,15,Fsince the council was established in
OL,16,F1973 - despite Reform winning 13 of
OL,17,Fthe 21 seats up for grabs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
