FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778259959
OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Major Labour
OL,4,Closses across North West
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats also made some
OL,7,Fgains, taking control from Stockport,
OL,8,Fwhich previously had no party
OL,9,Fmajority. They won two seats there,
OL,10,Fbringing the party's councillors to
OL,11,F33, while Labour lost five.
OL,13,FReform also saw gains in Chorley,
OL,14,Fgaining seven seats while Labour lost
OL,15,Feight, although the majority remains
OL,16,Fwith Sir Keir Starmer's party.
OL,18,FOldham Council remains in no overall
OL,19,Fcontrol, with Reform gaining 13 seats
OL,20,Fof the 20 seats up for grabs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778259959
OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Major Labour
OL,4,Closses across North West
OL,6,FIt was a similar story in Bolton -
OL,7,Fwhich remains without a party with a
OL,8,Fmajority - with Reform gaining nine
OL,9,Fand the Greens gaining three seats.
OL,11,FNationally, the initial results paint
OL,12,Fa bleak picture for the Prime
OL,13,FMinister, who has said he will not
OL,14,Fresign.
OL,16,FSir Keir Starmer said: "The results
OL,17,Fare tough, they are very tough, and
OL,18,Fthere's no sugarcoating it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778259959
OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Major Labour
OL,4,Closses across North West
OL,6,F"We have lost brilliant Labour
OL,7,Frepresentatives across the country,
OL,8,Fthese are people who put so much into
OL,9,Ftheir communities, so much into our
OL,10,Fparty.
OL,12,F"And that hurts, and it should hurt,
OL,13,Fand I take responsibility."
OL,15,FMeanwhile Andy Burnham pulled out of a
OL,16,Fkeynote speech he was set to give on
OL,17,Fthe morning after the local elections
OL,18,Famid speculation of a Labour
OL,19,Fleadership challenge to Sir Keir
OL,20,FStarmer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
