FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778259959
OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Major Labour
OL,4,Closses across North West
OL,6,FNigel Farage also said he is looking
OL,7,Fforward to hear the St Helens,
OL,8,FMerseyside results later today, where
OL,9,Fall 46 seats are up for grabs.
OL,11,FHe said: "These are areas where Boris
OL,12,FJohnson did well in 2019 in the red
OL,13,Fwall, but what you're going to see
OL,14,Ftoday from us is way way further than
OL,15,Fthat.
OL,17,F"I am convinced that this set of
OL,18,Felections is like our Becher's Brook.
OL,19,FYou have to clear Becher's Brook if
OL,20,Fyou want to land safely and win the
OL,21,FGrand National.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778259959
OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: Major Labour
OL,4,Closses across North West
OL,6,F"These are the most significant set of
OL,7,Felections between now and the general
OL,8,Felections and I think we're in a very
OL,9,Fgood place."
OL,11,FHe added Labour and the Conservatives
OL,12,Fwere being "wiped out" in their
OL,13,Ftraditional heartlands and said Reform
OL,14,Fwould bring a mix of new ideas and
OL,15,Fexperience.
OL,17,FHe said: "We all know that finances of
OL,18,Flocal councils all over the country
OL,19,Fare severely stretched. We are not
OL,20,Fpromising miracles but we are
OL,21,Fpromising good value for money."
